== 開發 ==

遊戲最初的版本在2006年釋出，持續開發至今。遊戲全部由塔恩·亞當斯和他的弟弟開發。兩人靠玩家的捐款生活。<ref name="GRose">{{cite web|title=Dwarf Fortress in 2013|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/195148/dwarf_fortress_in_2013.php?print=1|publisher=Gamasutra|accessdate=18 April 2014|author=Mike Rose|date=2 July 2013|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140511024509/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/195148/dwarf_fortress_in_2013.php?print=1|archivedate=2014-05-11}}</ref>

亞當斯曾表示這是個永遠開發不完的遊戲，他永遠會有新的東西想要加入。<ref name="IGEllsworth">{{cite web|last1=Ellsworth|first1=Craig|title=Dwarf Fortress: A game that will live forever?|url=http://indiegames.com/2013/03/dwarf_fortress_a_game_that_wil.html|publisher=IndieGames.com|accessdate=24 July 2014|date=24 March 2013|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130602135652/http://indiegames.com/2013/03/dwarf_fortress_a_game_that_wil.html|archivedate=2013-06-02}}</ref>

== 評價 ==

矮人要塞因為複雜的細節、自動產生的世界、[[開放世界|開放世界（open world）]]、{{Link-en|應變式遊戲|emergent gameplay|應變式遊戲（emergent gameplay）}}、困難的介面而受到矚目。<ref name="ATJohnston">{{cite web|last1=Johnston|first1=Casey|title=Dwarf Fortress: Ten hours with the most inscrutable video game of all time|url=http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2013/02/dwarf-fortress-ten-hours-with-the-most-inscrutable-video-game-of-all-time/|publisher=Ars Technica|accessdate=12 May 2014|date=25 February 2013|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812091921/http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2013/02/dwarf-fortress-ten-hours-with-the-most-inscrutable-video-game-of-all-time/|archivedate=2014-08-12}}</ref><ref name="IGNSpencer">{{cite web|title=A History of Roguelikes in 6 Free Games|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/12/26/a-history-of-roguelikes-in-6-free-games|publisher=IGN|accessdate=15 May 2014|author=Alex Spencer|date=26 Dec 2013|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413175539/http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/12/26/a-history-of-roguelikes-in-6-free-games|archivedate=2014-04-13}}</ref><ref name="NYTWiener">{{cite news|title=The Brilliance of Dwarf Fortress|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/24/magazine/the-brilliance-of-dwarf-fortress.html?pagewanted=all|work=The New York Times|accessdate=27 May 2012|author=Johah Weiner|date=21 July 2011|archive-date=2016-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160110152116/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/24/magazine/the-brilliance-of-dwarf-fortress.html?pagewanted=all|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Hastac">{{cite web|last1=Meeks|first1=Elijah|title=Procedural Humanities - An Interview with Tarn Adams, Creator of Dwarf Fortress|url=https://dhs.stanford.edu/algorithmic-literacy/an-interview-with-tarn-adams/|publisher=HASTAC|accessdate=19 June 2014|date=11 May 2010|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201150839/https://dhs.stanford.edu/algorithmic-literacy/an-interview-with-tarn-adams/|archivedate=2014-02-01|deadurl=yes}}</ref>有人將矮人要塞和模擬城市、模擬人生、Dungeon Keeper和NetHack等遊戲並列比較<ref name="PCGHogartya">{{cite journal|title=Dwarf Fortress diary: How seven drunks opened a portal to Hell p:1|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/how-seven-drunks-opened-a-portal-to-hell/|journal=PC Gamer|accessdate=17 April 2014|author=Steve Hogarty|date=August 2011|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140727062822/http://www.pcgamer.com/2011/08/09/dwarf-fortress-feature-how-seven-drunks-opened-a-portal-to-hell/|archivedate=2014-07-27}}</ref><ref name="NYTWiener" /><ref name="WMastrapa2">{{cite journal|last=Mastrapa|first=Gus|title=Elaborate, Sprawling Freeware Dwarf Fortress Updated|journal=Wired|date=April 2010|url=http://www.wired.com/2010/04/dwarf-fortress/|accessdate=14 May 2014|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140815183216/http://www.wired.com/2010/04/dwarf-fortress/|archivedate=2014-08-15|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

純文字的界面是遊戲難以上手的原因之一，但也強迫玩家必須靠自己的想像，而使遊戲更吸引人。<ref name="NYTWiener" /><ref name="PCGSenior">{{cite journal|last=Senior|first=Tom|title=Explore your Dwarf Fortress dungeon in Minecraft|journal=PC Gamer|date=September 2010|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/2010/09/24/explore-your-dwarf-fortress-dungeon-in-minecraft/|accessdate=14 May 2014|archive-date=2014-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140227230822/http://www.pcgamer.com/2010/09/24/explore-your-dwarf-fortress-dungeon-in-minecraft/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 影響 ==

矮人要塞影響了[[我的世界|我的世界]]，有些評論者認為我的世界是界面比較友善的矮人要塞<ref name="WGoldbergLarsson">{{cite journal|author1=Daniel Goldberg|author2=Linus Larsson|title=The Amazingly Unlikely Story of How Minecraft Was Born|journal=Wired|date=September 2013|url=http://www.wired.com/2013/11/minecraft-book/all/|accessdate=10 June 2014|archive-date=2016-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160117195519/http://www.wired.com/2013/11/minecraft-book/all/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NYTWiener" /><ref name="KPlunkett2">{{cite web|title=The PC's Best Free Games Right Now|url=http://kotaku.com/5687049/the-pcs-best-free-games-right-now|publisher=Kotaku|accessdate=15 May 2014|author=Luke Plunkett|date=12 November 2010|archive-date=2013-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224090808/http://kotaku.com/5687049/the-pcs-best-free-games-right-now|dead-url=no}}</ref>。亞當斯表示他很感激[[我的世界|我的世界]]的開發者有提到他的遊戲，而吸引更多玩家接觸<ref name="GRose" />。[[魔獸世界|魔獸世界]]中有出現向矮人要塞致敬的內容<ref name="NYTWiener" />。

2013年3月，紐約[[現代藝術博物館|現代藝術博物館]]展出了矮人要塞<ref name="GSMakuch">{{cite web|author1=Eddie Makuch|title=Museum of Modern Art opening game gallery|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/museum-of-modern-art-opening-game-gallery/1100-6400785/|publisher=Gamespot|accessdate=10 June 2014|date=29 November 2012|archive-date=2015-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150209083227/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/museum-of-modern-art-opening-game-gallery/1100-6400785/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。館長表示他對遊戲的漂亮的美感和難以置信的複雜度感到驚奇<ref name="NYTWiener" />。

[[超越光速|FTL:超光速]]（FTL: Faster Than Light）和發條帝國（Clockwork Empires）等遊戲都受到矮人要塞的啟發。<ref name="GIPearson">{{cite web|last1=Pearson|first1=Dan|title=Where I'm @: A Brief Look At The Resurgence of Roguelikes|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2013-01-30-where-im-a-brief-look-at-the-resurgence-of-roguelikes|publisher=GameIndustry.biz|accessdate=24 July 2014|date=31 January 2013|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140903135329/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2013-01-30-where-im-a-brief-look-at-the-resurgence-of-roguelikes|archivedate=2014-09-03|deadurl=no}}</ref>
